<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
        <title>tide chat room</title>
        <style>
            :root {
                --bg-1: #07111f;
                --bg-2: #12243d;
                --card: rgba(11, 19, 34, 0.78);
                --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
                --text: #e9eef8;
                --muted: #9fb0c8;
                --accent: #62d0ff;
                --accent-strong: #2aa8ff;
                --accent-contrast: #06111f;
                --success: #35d39a;
                --danger: #ff6b7a;
                --shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
            }

            * {
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }

            html, body {
                height: 100%;
            }

            body {
                margin: 0;
                font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "Noto Sans CJK SC", sans-serif;
                color: var(--text);
                background:
                    radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(98, 208, 255, 0.18), transparent 28%),
                    radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(53, 211, 154, 0.14), transparent 32%),
                    linear-gradient(145deg, var(--bg-1), var(--bg-2));
            }

            .page {
                min-height: 100%;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                padding: 32px 16px;
            }

            .shell {
                width: min(1120px, 100%);
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1.95fr;
                gap: 20px;
            }

            .panel {
                background: var(--card);
                border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
                border-radius: 24px;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
                backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            }

            .sidebar {
                padding: 28px;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 22px;
            }

            .brand {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .brand-mark {
                width: 54px;
                height: 54px;
                border-radius: 18px;
                display: grid;
                place-items: center;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
                color: var(--accent-contrast);
                font-weight: 800;
                letter-spacing: 0.04em;
                box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(42, 168, 255, 0.35);
            }

            .brand h1 {
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 30px;
                line-height: 1.1;
            }

            .brand p,
            .help-list,
            .hint {
                margin: 0;
                color: var(--muted);
                line-height: 1.7;
            }

            .info-card {
                padding: 18px;
                border-radius: 18px;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
                border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            }

            .status-row {
                display: flex;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 10px;
                margin-top: 12px;
            }

            .chip {
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 8px;
                padding: 8px 12px;
                border-radius: 999px;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
                color: var(--text);
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            .chip i {
                width: 8px;
                height: 8px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                background: var(--muted);
                display: inline-block;
            }

            .chip.ok i {
                background: var(--success);
            }

            .chip.warn i {
                background: #f5c24b;
            }

            .help-list {
                padding-left: 18px;
            }

            .help-list li + li {
                margin-top: 8px;
            }

            .chat-panel {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
                min-height: 720px;
                overflow: hidden;
            }

            .chat-header {
                padding: 24px 28px 18px;
                border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                gap: 16px;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .chat-header h2 {
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .chat-header .subtitle {
                margin-top: 6px;
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .message-area {
                padding: 20px 28px;
                overflow-y: auto;
                background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03));
            }

            .message-list {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 12px;
            }

            .empty-state {
                margin: auto;
                max-width: 440px;
                text-align: center;
                color: var(--muted);
                padding: 44px 16px;
            }

            .empty-state strong {
                display: block;
                color: var(--text);
                font-size: 18px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .message-item {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: flex-start;
            }

            .message-item.system {
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .bubble {
                max-width: min(760px, 100%);
                padding: 12px 16px;
                border-radius: 18px;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
                border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
                box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
                overflow-wrap: anywhere;
            }

            .bubble.system {
                background: rgba(98, 208, 255, 0.12);
                color: #d8f2ff;
                font-size: 14px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .bubble .meta {
                display: flex;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 8px;
                align-items: center;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .bubble .name {
                color: #ffffff;
                font-weight: 600;
            }

            .bubble .content {
                white-space: pre-wrap;
                line-height: 1.7;
                color: var(--text);
            }

            .composer {
                padding: 20px 28px 28px;
                border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
                display: grid;
                gap: 12px;
            }

            .form-grid {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr auto;
                gap: 12px;
            }

            .field {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 8px;
            }

            .field label {
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            .field input {
                width: 100%;
                min-height: 48px;
                border-radius: 14px;
                border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
                color: var(--text);
                padding: 0 14px;
                font-size: 15px;
                outline: none;
                transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            }

            .field input::placeholder {
                color: rgba(159, 176, 200, 0.8);
            }

            .field input:focus {
                border-color: rgba(98, 208, 255, 0.8);
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(42, 168, 255, 0.16);
            }

            .actions {
                display: flex;
                align-items: end;
            }

            .btn {
                min-height: 48px;
                border: 0;
                border-radius: 14px;
                padding: 0 18px;
                font-size: 15px;
                font-weight: 700;
                cursor: pointer;
                transition: transform 0.15s ease, opacity 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
            }

            .btn:hover {
                transform: translateY(-1px);
            }

            .btn:active {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            .btn-primary {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
                color: var(--accent-contrast);
                box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(42, 168, 255, 0.28);
            }

            .btn-secondary {
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
                color: var(--text);
                border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            }

            .btn:disabled {
                cursor: not-allowed;
                opacity: 0.55;
                transform: none;
                box-shadow: none;
            }

            .helper-row {
                display: flex;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: space-between;
                gap: 12px;
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            .helper-row strong {
                color: var(--text);
            }

            @media (max-width: 920px) {
                .shell {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                }

                .chat-panel {
                    min-height: 640px;
                }

                .form-grid {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                }

                .actions {
                    align-items: stretch;
                }

                .btn {
                    width: 100%;
                }
            }

            @media (max-width: 560px) {
                .page {
                    padding: 12px;
                }

                .sidebar,
                .chat-header,
                .message-area,
                .composer {
                    padding-left: 16px;
                    padding-right: 16px;
                }

                .brand h1 {
                    font-size: 26px;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        var websocket = null;
        var connected = false;

        function escapeHtml(text) {
            return String(text)
                .replace(/&/g, '&amp;')
                .replace(/</g, '&lt;')
                .replace(/>/g, '&gt;')
                .replace(/"/g, '&quot;')
                .replace(/'/g, '&#39;');
        }

        function scrollToBottom() {
            var container = document.getElementById("message");
            container.scrollTop = container.scrollHeight;
        }

        function write_msg(msg) {
            var container = document.getElementById("message");
            var empty = document.getElementById("empty-state");
            if(empty) {
                empty.style.display = "none";
            }
            container.insertAdjacentHTML("beforeend", msg);
            scrollToBottom();
        }

        function writeSystemMsg(text) {
            write_msg('<div class="message-item system"><div class="bubble system">' + escapeHtml(text) + '</div></div>');
        }

        function writeChatMsg(time, name, msg) {
            write_msg(
                '<div class="message-item"><div class="bubble">' +
                    '<div class="meta"><span class="name">' + escapeHtml(name) + '</span><span>' + escapeHtml(time) + '</span></div>' +
                    '<div class="content">' + escapeHtml(msg) + '</div>' +
                '</div></div>'
            );
        }

        function setConnectedState(isConnected) {
            connected = isConnected;
            var status = document.getElementById('connection-status');
            var sendBtn = document.getElementById('send-btn');
            var loginBtn = document.getElementById('login-btn');

            if(isConnected) {
                status.innerHTML = '<i></i> 已连接';
                sendBtn.disabled = false;
                loginBtn.disabled = true;
            } else {
                status.innerHTML = '<i></i> 未连接';
                sendBtn.disabled = true;
                loginBtn.disabled = false;
            }
        }

        function login() {
            var nameInput = document.getElementById('tname');
            var name = nameInput.value.trim();
            if(!name) {
                writeSystemMsg('请先填写昵称，再点击登录。');
                nameInput.focus();
                return;
            }

            if(websocket && websocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {
                websocket.close();
            }

            writeSystemMsg('正在连接聊天室，请稍候...');
            websocket = new WebSocket("ws://127.0.0.1:8071/tide/chat");

            websocket.onerror = function() {
                writeSystemMsg("连接发生错误，请确认服务已启动。");
            }

            websocket.onopen = function() {
                var o = {};
                o.type = "login_request";
                o.name = name;
                websocket.send(JSON.stringify(o));
            }

            websocket.onmessage= function(e) {
                //alert("onmessage " + e.data);
                var o = JSON.parse(e.data);
                if(o.type == "user_enter") {
                    writeSystemMsg("[" + o.time + "][" + o.name + "] 加入聊天室");
                } else if(o.type == "user_leave") {
                    writeSystemMsg("[" + o.time + "][" + o.name + "] 离开聊天室");
                } else if(o.type == "msg") {
                    writeChatMsg(o.time, o.name, o.msg);
                } else if(o.type == "login_response") {
                    writeSystemMsg("[" + o.result + "][" + o.msg + "]");
                    if(String(o.result).toLowerCase() == "ok" || String(o.result) == "0" || String(o.result) == "200") {
                        setConnectedState(true);
                        document.getElementById('msg').focus();
                    }
                }
            }

            websocket.onclose= function() {
                setConnectedState(false);
                writeSystemMsg("服务器已断开连接。");
            }
        }

        function sendmsg() {
            if(!websocket || websocket.readyState !== WebSocket.OPEN) {
                writeSystemMsg('当前还没有连接成功，请先登录。');
                return;
            }

            var msgInput = document.getElementById('msg');
            var message = msgInput.value.trim();
            if(!message) {
                msgInput.focus();
                return;
            }

            var o = {}
            o.type = "send_request";
            o.msg = message;
            websocket.send(JSON.stringify(o));
            msgInput.value = "";
            msgInput.focus();
        }

        function initPage() {
            setConnectedState(false);
            document.getElementById('msg').addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
                if(e.key === 'Enter') {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    sendmsg();
                }
            });

            document.getElementById('tname').addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
                if(e.key === 'Enter') {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    login();
                }
            });
        }
    </script>
    <body onload="initPage()">
        <div class="page">
            <div class="shell">
                <aside class="panel sidebar">
                    <div class="brand">
                        <div class="brand-mark">聊</div>
                        <h1>tide chat room</h1>
                        <p>一个轻量的聊天室页面，适合快速接入和演示。界面会尽量把关键信息摆在前面，减少操作成本。</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="chip" id="connection-status"><i></i> 未连接</div>
                        <div class="status-row">
                            <div class="chip ok"><i></i> 支持回车发送</div>
                            <div class="chip warn"><i></i> 消息会自动滚动</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="info-card">
                        <p style="margin:0 0 10px 0;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">使用提示</p>
                        <ol class="help-list">
                            <li>先填昵称，点登录后再发消息。</li>
                            <li>输入框里按 Enter 也可以直接发送。</li>
                            <li>如果提示断开，请确认服务端已经启动。</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </aside>

                <main class="panel chat-panel">
                    <header class="chat-header">
                        <div>
                            <h2>聊天室</h2>
                            <div class="subtitle">登录后即可开始聊天，消息会实时显示在下方。</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="chip"><i></i> WebSocket</div>
                    </header>

                    <section class="message-area" id="message">
                        <div class="empty-state" id="empty-state">
                            <strong>还没有消息</strong>
                            <div>登录后，这里会显示进出提醒和聊天内容。先试着输入一个昵称开始吧。</div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="composer">
                        <div class="form-grid">
                            <div class="field">
                                <label for="tname">昵称</label>
                                <input id="tname" type="text" placeholder="例如：小明" autocomplete="nickname" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="field">
                                <label for="msg">聊天信息</label>
                                <input id="msg" type="text" placeholder="输入要发送的内容，按 Enter 可直接发送" autocomplete="off" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="actions">
                                <button id="login-btn" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="login()">登录</button>
                                <span style="width:10px;"></span>
                                <button id="send-btn" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="sendmsg()" disabled>发送</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="helper-row">
                            <div>建议先登录，再发送消息。</div>
                            <div>如果页面空白，通常是服务端未启动。</div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </main>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>